                            <comment id="15080433" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 3 Jan 2016 13:54:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One of the used 4 fonts is broken (Tc5, cmti10). I tried to skip the unknown operand but ran into another exception. Looks like we have to put some more effort into the parser to support at least some of the corrupted fonts, either by skipping malformed data or by replacing such fonts.&lt;br/&gt;
Fontforge also complains about the font.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
